<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://blog.didierstevens.com/2007/05/07/is-your-pc-virus-free-get-it-infected-here/" class="external free" title="http://blog.didierstevens.com/2007/05/07/is-your-pc-virus-free-get-it-infected-here/" rel="nofollow">http://blog.didierstevens.com/2007/05/07/is-your-pc-virus-free-get-it-infected-here/</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.viruslist.com/en/analysis?pubid=191968025" class="external text" title="http://www.viruslist.com/en/analysis?pubid=191968025" rel="nofollow">"Malware Evolution: Mac OS X Vulnerabilities 2005-2006"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Kaspersky_Lab" title="Kaspersky Lab">Kaspersky Lab</a>. 2006-07-24<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.viruslist.com/en/analysis?pubid=191968025" class="external free" title="http://www.viruslist.com/en/analysis?pubid=191968025" rel="nofollow">http://www.viruslist.com/en/analysis?pubid=191968025</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on August 19, 2006</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Malware+Evolution%3A+Mac+OS+X+Vulnerabilities+2005-2006&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2006-07-24&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BKaspersky+Lab%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.viruslist.com%2Fen%2Fanalysis%3Fpubid%3D191968025&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Computer_virus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
