<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMcAfee">McAfee. <a href="http://math-www.uni-paderborn.de/~axel/bliss/mcafee_press.html" class="external text" title="http://math-www.uni-paderborn.de/~axel/bliss/mcafee_press.html" rel="nofollow">"McAfee discovers first Linux virus"</a>. <i>news article</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://math-www.uni-paderborn.de/~axel/bliss/mcafee_press.html" class="external free" title="http://math-www.uni-paderborn.de/~axel/bliss/mcafee_press.html" rel="nofollow">http://math-www.uni-paderborn.de/~axel/bliss/mcafee_press.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=McAfee+discovers+first+Linux+virus&amp;rft.atitle=news+article&amp;rft.aulast=McAfee&amp;rft.au=McAfee&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmath-www.uni-paderborn.de%2F%7Eaxel%2Fbliss%2Fmcafee_press.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Computer_virus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
