<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSzor2005">Szor, Peter (2005). <i>The Art of Computer Virus Research and Defense</i>. Boston: Addison-Wesley. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0321304543" class="internal">ISBN 0321304543</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Art+of+Computer+Virus+Research+and+Defense&amp;rft.aulast=Szor&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter&amp;rft.au=Szor%2C+Peter&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.place=Boston&amp;rft.pub=Addison-Wesley&amp;rft.isbn=0321304543&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Computer_virus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
